---
// src/components/Benefits.astro
---
<section id="beneficios" class="benefits">
  <div class="benefits-container">
    <div class="benefits-header">
      <div class="benefits-badge">Beneficios</div>
      <h2>Todo lo que necesitás para <span>escalar tus ventas</span></h2>
      <p class="benefits-subtitle">Potenciá tu negocio con herramientas inteligentes que trabajan por vos las 24 horas.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="benefit-card featured">
        <div class="benefit-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Respuestas Instantáneas</h3>
        <p>Respondé en menos de 3 segundos a cada consulta. No pierdas más clientes por demoras.</p>
        <div class="benefit-metric">
          <span class="metric-value">3s</span>
          <span class="metric-label">tiempo de respuesta promedio</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon purple-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87m-4-12a4 4 0 010 7.75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Clasificación de Prospectos</h3>
        <p>Identificá automáticamente prospectos calientes, tibios y fríos. Enfocá tu energía donde importa.</p>
        <div class="prospect-bars">
          <div class="prospect-bar"><div class="bar-label">Calientes</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill hot" style="width:85%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="prospect-bar"><div class="bar-label">Tibios</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill warm" style="width:60%"></div></div></div>
          <div class="prospect-bar"><div class="bar-label">Fríos</div><div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill cold" style="width:30%"></div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon green-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bandeja Unificada</h3>
        <p>WhatsApp, Instagram y Messenger en un solo lugar. Gestioná todo sin cambiar de app.</p>
        <div class="channel-icons">
          <div class="channel whatsapp"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M8 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
          <div class="channel instagram"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg></div>
          <div class="channel messenger"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon amber-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seguridad y Privacidad</h3>
        <p>Tus datos protegidos con encriptación de extremo a extremo y cumplimiento normativo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon blue-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Chatbots Personalizables</h3>
        <p>Creá flujos de conversación adaptados a tu negocio. Tu chatbot habla como vos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <div class="benefit-icon rose-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28"><path d="M16 8v8m-4-5v5m-4-2v2m-2 4h16a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Reportes y Analíticas</h3>
        <p>Métricas en tiempo real sobre conversiones, tiempos de respuesta y rendimiento.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits { padding: 7rem 0; background: #ffffff; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .benefits::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -200px; right: -200px; width: 500px; height: 500px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(21,198,59,0.03) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
  .benefits-container { max-width: 1200px; width: 90%; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .benefits-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .benefits-badge { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58,61,238,0.08), rgba(99,102,241,0.15)); color: var(--color-primary-blue); padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border: 1px solid rgba(58,61,238,0.1); }
  h2 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.2; color: var(--color-text-dark); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  h2 span { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-blue), #6366f1); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
  .benefits-subtitle { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-medium); max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .benefits-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .benefit-card { background: white; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; border-radius: 20px; padding: 2.25rem 2rem; transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .benefit-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary-blue), var(--color-primary-green)); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.35s; }
  .benefit-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); border-color: rgba(58,61,238,0.12); }
  .benefit-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
  .benefit-card.featured { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b 0%, #312e81 100%); border-color: transparent; color: white; }
  .benefit-card.featured h3 { color: white; }
  .benefit-card.featured p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }
  .benefit-card.featured .benefit-icon { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: #a5b4fc; }
  .benefit-card.featured:hover { box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(30,27,75,0.3); }
  .benefit-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58,61,238,0.08), rgba(58,61,238,0.15)); color: var(--color-primary-blue); transition: transform 0.35s; }
  .benefit-card:hover .benefit-icon { transform: scale(1.1); }
  .purple-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(139,92,246,0.08), rgba(139,92,246,0.15)); color: #8b5cf6; }
  .green-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21,198,59,0.08), rgba(21,198,59,0.15)); color: var(--color-primary-green); }
  .amber-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,158,11,0.08), rgba(245,158,11,0.15)); color: #f59e0b; }
  .blue-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58,61,238,0.08), rgba(58,61,238,0.15)); color: var(--color-primary-blue); }
  .rose-icon { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244,63,94,0.08), rgba(244,63,94,0.15)); color: #f43f5e; }
  .benefit-card h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text-dark); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .benefit-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--color-text-medium); margin: 0; }
  .benefit-metric { margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; padding-top: 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
  .metric-value { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #a5b4fc; line-height: 1; }
  .metric-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.4; }
  .prospect-bars { margin-top: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .prospect-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .bar-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text-medium); min-width: 65px; text-align: left; }
  .bar-track { flex: 1; height: 6px; background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 10px; }
  .bar-fill.hot { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f43f5e, #fb7185); }
  .bar-fill.warm { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #fbbf24); }
  .bar-fill.cold { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #60a5fa); }
  .channel-icons { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .channel { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: transform 0.3s; }
  .channel:hover { transform: scale(1.15); }
  .channel.whatsapp { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.1); color: #25d366; }
  .channel.instagram { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(131,58,180,0.1), rgba(253,29,29,0.1)); color: #c13584; }
  .channel.messenger { background: rgba(0,132,255,0.1); color: #0084ff; }
  @media (max-width: 992px) { .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; } }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .benefits-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .benefits { padding: 4rem 0; } h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; } .benefits-subtitle { font-size: 1rem; } }
</style>
